In Australia, this Standard does not apply to fixed electrical installations forming part of the following:
(a) electrical installations as per AS/NZS 3000;
(b) shows and carnival installations as per AS/NZS 3002;
(c) construction and demolition installations as per AS/NZS 3012;
(d) marina installations as per AS/NZS 3004.1; or
(e) parts of other installations not intended to supply electricity to a connectable electrical installation.
In New Zealand, this Standard does not apply to the following:
(i) marina installations; or
(ii) parts of other installations not intended for use to supply electricity to a connectable electrical installation.
